{"tid":2006504,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"（綠帽俠又出動）謝東閔獨自搬入新愛巢","createTime":"2020-05-07T22:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T00:35:12.000Z","uid":57542,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"33c3f18a6b4e5ad3158aaa35fe2927574181fa04","tid":2006504,"uid":57542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T22:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XW9D3BW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXW9D3BW.jpg&h=f647dec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TWFDjah.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTWFDjah.jpg&h=28fc035a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上周經歷完最冷的一天，「綠帽俠」謝東閔曾在記者會上力撐出軌女友朱智賢，指因為自己太忙忽略了女友，令對方一時迷失而做錯事搭上人夫黎振燁，更在記招上公開承諾會陪對方共渡難關。記者會上的暖男舉動，令謝東閔被封「綠帽俠」，當大眾都以為他跟朱智賢真的可以共渡難關時，就有傳媒拍得謝東閔默默搬離跟朱智賢位於深井的愛巢。"},{"pid":"ab5672817f84a999a2f777858f16e9884b088d7a","tid":2006504,"uid":57542,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T22:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0PdJvhJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0PdJvhJ.jpg&h=4ce0d947&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"067da6b4854ab4dc9a705f547323d02fbe017654","tid":2006504,"uid":356914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T22:45:29.000Z","msg":"屌夠就好走啦 唔好埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112190a0766556264670c8698032c63201517b92","tid":2006504,"uid":57542,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T22:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/y0GmS0L.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"557f84ebe8388db59c3dba8c679948467d6e59aa","tid":2006504,"uid":57542,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T22:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/UBpS6qx.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"b22df1804824b8031f9215717b92cba9d51f73d8","tid":2006504,"uid":1188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"s